nursing Library. The headquarters, which will be open every
night from 8-9 beginning Mon-
‘day, will provide information
and campaign materials. Anyone interested in learning about
polyester and/or working on
the campaign are tried to drop
by the group’s chairman, Robin universe.
Ken sherman, who is chairman of the Romney campaign,
says that the telephone drive
conducted last week on Young
